        "title": "Understanding Cold Sensations",
        "content": "Cold sensations can indicate various health conditions. They may be caused by environmental factors or underlying medical issues."
      },
      {
        "title": "Common Symptoms Associated with Cold Sensations",
        "content": "- Shivering\n- Numbness in extremities\n- Pale skin\n- Slow heart rate"
      },
      {
        "title": "Implications of Cold Sensations",
        "content": "- May indicate hypothermia\n- Could signal poor circulation\n- Often linked to anxiety or stress\n- Requires assessment for underlying conditions"
      }
    ]
  }
}
